thread.title: Jen Eady
thread.title_full: Paper Divas reviewed by Jen Eady

author: Jen Eady
title: Jen Eady
text: I am very impressed with Paper Divas! Such a fabulous range of choices and with the ability to adjust the invitations to my liking made it so simple and easy. I had two birthday party invites to do, I did them in less than ten minutes, the order was processed and my package was delivered before 10am the next morning! The kids love them and we have received many wonderful comments about them. Thank you! I couldn't have asked for better service!
